__NAME__ purpose
use the "fortune" program to display random saying
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<row>
	<entry>
		<arg choice='plain'>short</arg>
	</entry>
	<entry>Yes</entry><entry></entry>
	<entry>0</entry>
	<entry>Display only short (less than 160 characters) fortune sayings?</entry>
</row>
